code: @Override protected Mono<Health> doHealthCheck(Health.Builder builder) {     Mono<Document> buildInfo = this.reactiveMongoTemplate.executeCommand("{ buildInfo: 1 }").     return buildInfo.map((document) -> up(builder, document)). }
private Health up(Health.Builder builder, Document document) {     return builder.up().withDetail("version", document.getString("version")).build(). }
